<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes and slope erosion rather than fire primarily disturb stands. Fires are likely to occur only in late season or in extremely dry years. Fires are unlikely to affect stands negatively because of the extensive underground rhizome system.</div>
